---
// About FOOD STAND
---

<section class="about fade-in" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="deco-circle"></div>

    <div class="section-label">
      <div class="section-label-num">02</div>
      <div class="section-label-line"></div>
      <div class="section-label-name">ABOUT</div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="big-title about-title">
      Our<br />
      <span class="big-title-italic">food</span>,<br />
      Your event.
    </h2>

    <div class="jp-sub">FOOD STAND について</div>

    <div class="message-block">
      <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
      <p class="message">
        選ばれる味と<br />
        <span class="message-accent">確かな対応</span>で、<br />
        イベントの成功に貢献する<br />
        フードパートナーを<br />
        目指します。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="keypoints">
      <div class="keypoint">
        <div class="keypoint-num">01</div>
        <div class="keypoint-jp">4つの<br />ブランド</div>
      </div>
      <div class="keypoint">
        <div class="keypoint-num">02</div>
        <div class="keypoint-jp">大型<br />実績多数</div>
      </div>
      <div class="keypoint">
        <div class="keypoint-num">03</div>
        <div class="keypoint-jp">1都4県<br />対応</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 100px 0 60px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .deco-circle {
    position: absolute;
    top: -30px;
    right: -60px;
    width: 140px;
    height: 140px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-bluegray-light), var(--color-bluegray));
    opacity: 0.3;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .about-title {
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 54px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .jp-sub {
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-family: var(--font-serif-jp);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .jp-sub::before {
    content: "—— ";
    color: var(--color-bluegray-medium);
    margin-right: 4px;
  }
  .message-block {
    margin-top: 50px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .quote-mark {
    font-family: var(--font-serif-en);
    font-size: 90px;
    line-height: 0.7;
    color: var(--color-bluegray-light);
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin-left: -8px;
    margin-bottom: -20px;
  }
  .message {
    font-family: var(--font-serif-jp);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 22px;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .message-accent {
    color: var(--color-bluegray-medium);
  }
  .keypoints {
    margin-top: 50px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .keypoint {
    flex: 1;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 18px 4px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: #FFFFFF;
  }
  .keypoint-num {
    font-family: var(--font-serif-en);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--color-bluegray-dark);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .keypoint-jp {
    font-family: var(--font-serif-jp);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.4;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
</style>
